$$

$$
 \Delta^&amp;#43; DOU = \lambda \times DNU
$$

$$
 \Delta^- DOU = \gamma \times DOU
$$

当均衡态时，有 $\Delta^&amp;#43; DOU = \Delta^- DOU$

即 $\lambda \times DNU = \gamma \times DOU$

$$
 DAU = (1&amp;#43;\frac{\lambda}{\gamma})\times DNU
$$

